{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1306989, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那种只知道借钱不打工还钱，或者借裸贷之类的 ，还奢侈消费的，只能叫它们nt 不能叫他们穷人", "timestamp": 1616329746, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1306992, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#政治相关#", "timestamp": 1616329776, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1306997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对于穷人而言，借钱翻身的多还是借钱把自己陷进去的多呢？", "timestamp": 1616329837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307005, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在有助学金和国家贷款。另外堵不如疏没有花呗就会有地下交易。", "timestamp": 1616329994, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307011, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "借钱翻身的反面就是还不上钱被压垮。贫困学生应该可以申请国家贷款，政府贴息。", "timestamp": 1616330059, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不太清楚宣布成功之后扶贫政策会怎么样，反正你愿意打工扶贫人员都是开心的。", "timestamp": 1616330194, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 的确有贷款，但是一般也就几千块。可设想一下，如果一个大学生的家庭没有给他任何生活费，靠这点国家统一的助学贷就能生存下去吗", "timestamp": 1616330272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 多一条借钱的路子，穷人就能多一分周旋的余地", "timestamp": 1616330338, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在脱贫的标准是人均年收入四千左右。四千块，在任何一个省会城市够生存多久？", "timestamp": 1616330477, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1307065, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 257026, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 能。cz能告诉你真的可以。", "timestamp": 1616330487, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 0, "pid": 257026, "reply": 10, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "禁止大学生使用花呗和借呗到底是对穷人有利还是有害？（富人可能用不到花呗） 我表哥几年前上大学的时候，家里没钱，就是靠支付宝和银行卡先借钱花，然后自己再打工赚钱去还，现在穷人借钱越来越难了，想借钱翻身都难。", "timestamp": 1616329599, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616330488, "url": "", "vote": {}}}